metadata.description:
Within the monochromatic manga frame, Kaito crouches, his gaze meeting the viewer's. Donned in a heroic suit and mask, there's an undeniable charm in his presence. Despite the colder tones, Kaito radiates warmth and resilience, a testament to the strength inherent in his character. 

A moving, optimistic portrayal in the subtle nuances of black and white.
metadata.name: Kaito the Degen #1/4
